    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Wizards who choose to become illusionists specialize in spells from the school of illusion. Illusionists lack the raw power of most other wizards but rely instead on trickery and creativity to overcome their enemies. Unlike other wizards, an illusionist can count on their illusions deceiving most creatures, and can even add magical force to their illusions to directly harm and hinder their enemies.</p><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>Expanded Spell List</caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.vZbMv43ZhTIR0kuW]{Illusion Specialization}, Bonus Spell: @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.WpJfAWT5r4gpvN85]{Silent Image (Illusionist)}</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.CATr5HOQgN67Aciv]{Masterful Illusions}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.hg1255dcMD2hQTGz]{Phantom Force}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.K3soXTx6xqaMJv86]{Phantom Barrage}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8KxLYpEVn8TsAg3i]{Phantom Grasp}</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.SPv7HV15Lu5llCuU]{Floating Magician}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.fQxYa5USyngg0253]{Forceful Image}</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.7UWuxrYn9y0gf8YZ]{Illusionist's Eye}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.nUVANwtLv79t2Jtx]{Illusory Reality}</td></tr></tbody></table>",
